    <description>as defined by perometry using rigorous measurement protocols. Bilateral arm measurements will be obtained using the Perometer (Model 350 NT Perometer, Per-System) and the L-Dex U400 (Impedimed, Brisbane, Australia) for bioimpedance measurements.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
